#:: ''[[clamor|Clamor]] '''ad''' [[caelus|caelum]] [[volvere|volvendus]].'' ([[cf.]] ''[[tollere|tollitur]] [[in#Latin|in]] [[caelus|caelum]] [[clamor]]'')
#:: '''''Ad''' [[caelus|caelum]][[-que|que]] [[ferre|ferat]] [[flamma]]e [[fulgur]]a [[rursum]].''
